---
import { Shield, TrendingUp, Award, Check } from 'lucide-svelte';
---
<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="container-tight">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="eyebrow">Kenapa Menantu Resort</span>
      <h2 class="heading-title mt-4">
        Tiga Pilar <em>yang Menjaga</em><br/>Aset Anda Selamanya.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-6">
        Bukan sekadar villa — ini paket lengkap legalitas, operasional, dan return.
        Tiga hal yang biasanya jadi mimpi buruk investor, kami selesaikan.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-10">
      <article class="card accent-line p-10 md:p-12">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-forest-500 text-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <Shield size="32" strokeWidth="1.5" />
        </div>
        <span class="eyebrow text-forest-500 mb-3 block">Pilar 1 · Legalitas</span>
        <h3 class="heading text-2xl mb-4">SHM, Atas Nama Pribadi</h3>
        <p class="text-body text-ink-500 mb-6">
          Sertifikat Hak Milik — status legal tertinggi di Indonesia. Bukan Hak Pakai,
          bukan sewa. Aset tangible seumur hidup, bisa diwariskan ke generasi berikutnya.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Clean & clear, dijamin bebas sengketa</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Izin komersial resmi untuk运营 hotel</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Notaris independen, akad terikat</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card accent-line p-10 md:p-12">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-forest-500 text-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <Award size="32" strokeWidth="1.5" />
        </div>
        <span class="eyebrow text-forest-500 mb-3 block">Pilar 2 · Operasional</span>
        <h3 class="heading text-2xl mb-4">Dikelola Sahid, 50+ Tahun</h3>
        <p class="text-body text-ink-500 mb-6">
          Tim Sahid Hotel & Resort yang sudah mengelola 20+ hotel bintang 4-5
          akan menjalankan villa Anda setiap hari. Standar hospitality internasional
          tanpa Anda harus pusing.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Housekeeping & maintenance harian</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Marketing OTA + corporate</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Customer service 24/7</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card accent-line p-10 md:p-12">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-forest-500 text-gold-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <TrendingUp size="32" strokeWidth="1.5" />
        </div>
        <span class="eyebrow text-forest-500 mb-3 block">Pilar 3 · Return</span>
        <h3 class="heading text-2xl mb-4">ROI 10% Guarantee</h3>
        <p class="text-body text-ink-500 mb-6">
          Jaminan Return On Investment minimal 10% per tahun untuk 2 tahun pertama —
          melindungi cashflow awal. Ditambah capital gain 15-30% dalam 15 tahun.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> 70% profit share untuk pemilik</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Laporan bulanan transparan</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><Check size="16" class="text-gold-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" /> Capital gain naik 28% YoY</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
